Our business













Minerals Australia
The Minerals Australia asset group includes operated assets in Western Australia, Queensland, New South Wales and South Australia. Our assets focus on copper, iron ore, coal and nickel.
Discover more










Minerals Americas
The Minerals Americas asset group includes projects, operated and non-operated assets in Canada, Chile, Peru, United States, Colombia and Brazil. Our assets and projects focus on copper, zinc, iron ore, coal and potash.
Discover more










Petroleum
Our Petroleum unit comprises conventional and unconventional oil and gas operations, and includes exploration, development, production and marketing activities in the United States, Australia and Trinidad and Tobago.
Discover more














Marketing
Marketing is an independent core business of BHP. It is the link between BHP’s global operations and our global customers.
Discover more










