BHP - Wikipedia






















 






BHP

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from BHP Billiton)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Billiton" redirects here. For the Indonesian island formerly known as Billiton, see Belitung.

BHP





Type

Public


Traded as
LSE: BLT
NYSE: BHP
NYSE: BBL
ASX: BHP
JSE: BIL
